= SDL_SensorOpen =
Open a sensor for use.


== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_Sensor *SDLCALL SDL_SensorOpen(int device_index);
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''device_index'''
|The sensor to open
|}

== Return Value ==
A [[SDL_Sensor]] sensor object, or NULL if an error occurred.

